NAME
    DBIx::Class::Schema::Critic - Critique a database schema for best
    practices

VERSION
    version 0.001

ATTRIBUTES
  schema
    A DBIx::Class::Schema object you wish to "critique". Only settable at
    construction time.

  policies
    A reference to an array of DBIx::Class::Schema::Critic::Policy consumers
    that will be applied during "critique". Can be set at construction or
    via the "policies" accessor method.

METHODS
  add_policy
    Adds a DBIx::Class::Schema::Critic::Policy consumer to "policies".

  critique
    Arguments: *$schema?*
    Return value: none

    Runs the *$schema* through the DBIx::Class::Schema::Critic engine using
    all the policies that have been loaded. If no *$schema* is provided then
    the "schema" attribute is used.

